reviewText: This DVD teaching kids about garden work and how and what to plant and when and where.  They do things together as a family which is also nice. It teaches kids about nature and the seasons when and what to plant.  Love it.  Also shows kids what games to play outdoors.
My daughter really loves watching Caillou and this is a nice DVD collection of Caillou episodes. She loves the outdoors so this is perfect for her to see Caillou in outdoor settings.

This DVD contains six episodes from the Caillou cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Caillou Can Compost
2. Caillou's Tree
3. Caillou Saves Water
4. Blueberry Point
5. Class Pet
6. In the Garden
